This package was built to be unzipped at C:\ If you place it
elsewhere, globally define SNODIR to point to the location (or define
SNOPATH).

The \bin directory contains an sdb.bat file to run the debugger, and a
timing script.  Please consider running the speed test:
	timing.bat >timing.txt
and attaching timing.txt to an email to timing@snobol4.org
